{"tid":2155077,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍城警署疑扯錯旗 區旗涉違例大過國旗 國旗陳舊褪色","createTime":"2020-08-13T13:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T13:48:28.000Z","uid":269724,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"004cb45fde1a3ad6f5d72c453a152e711684e1c3","tid":2155077,"uid":269724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lFjltt5nnv_XbyeE7RcTqgsqU-A=/1950x1097/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XRI5A3O4E5DYFIGMMH4PPVREBE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlFjltt5nnv_XbyeE7RcTqgsqU-A%3D%2F1950x1097%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXRI5A3O4E5DYFIGMMH4PPVREBE.png&h=738a682a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍城警署升旗出現「妹仔大過主人婆」現象，《蘋果》發現警署升掛起的國旗與區旗，區旗大過國旗，國旗亦相對褪色，傍晚所見仍未被糾正，《蘋果》正就事件向警方查詢，暫未回覆。<br />\n<br />\n2008年，時任立法會議員劉皇發曾就懸掛國旗問題向政府質詢，時任政務司司長唐英年回覆，《區旗及區徽條例》列明，特區凡國旗與區旗同時懸掛時，應當將國旗置於較突出的位置。基於以上規定，在實際執行上，當平列懸掛國旗和區旗時，國旗在右，區旗在左，而區旗應小於國旗；如國旗、區旗與其他旗幟同時懸掛，須把國旗置於中心或較顯著的位置。<br />\n<br />\n政府總部禮賓處有更詳細說明，國旗與區旗同時或並列升掛、使用時，區旗應小於國旗，亦不得展示或使用破損、污損、褪色或不合規格的旗幟。有關內容同見於教育局「認識國旗、國歌與區旗」章節。<br />\n<br />\n今次非警隊首次出現升旗失誤，今年一月初旺角警署、以及2018年新界北總區警察總部都曾被發現倒掛國旗，同年大嶼山北警署也曾被發現倒掛區旗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/KOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FKOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR8SEfYUahrxQZPnd5z%2FpXIo%3D&h=c03f4424\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FKOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA%2F&h=42ea0f54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/KOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA/</a>"},{"pid":"a2ff06479f70a187b35a34574c0c901cefa84574","tid":2155077,"uid":269724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:37